* {{ill|Kushiyama Kofun|ja|櫛山古墳|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Tenjinyama Kofun|ja|大和天神山古墳|lt=Tenjinyama Kofun|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Shibuya Mukoyama Kofun|ja|渋谷向山古墳|lt=Tomb of Emperor Keikō|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Hashihaka Kofun|ja|箸墓古墳|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Hibara Shrine|ja|檜原神社|lt=Hibara Shrine (Ōmiwa Shrine Area)|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Anashi Izasu Hyozu Shrine|ja|穴師坐兵主神社|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Yatogi Shrine|ja|夜都伎神社|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Mount Miwa|ja|三輪山|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Ōmiwa Shrine|ja|大神神社|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Takenouchi Moated Settlement|ja|竹之内環濠集落|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Kayō Moated Settlement|ja|萱生環濠集落|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Shiki Mizugaki Palace|ja|磯城瑞籬宮|qq=draft|qq=draft}}

