* {{ill|Kayō Moated Settlement|ja|萱生環濠集落|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kayō Moated Settlement|qq=}}
* {{ill|Shiki Mizugaki Palace|ja|磯城瑞籬宮|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shiki Mizugaki Palace|qq=}}

